title: Joe Henderson - Ballads & Blues
description:
Joe Henderson
Ballads & Blues

1 Lazy Afternoon 5:30 (J. Latouche - J. Moross)
Joe Henderson - tenor saxaphone
Steve Kuhn - piano
Steve Swallow - bass
Pete LaRoca - drums
Recorded on May 19, 1965
Originally issued on the Pete LaRoca album Basra

2 La Mesha 9:05 (Kenny Dorham)
Joe Henderson - tenor saxaphone
Kenny Dorham - trumpet
McCoy Tyner - Piano
Butch Warren - bass
Pete LaRoca - drums
Recorded on June 3, 1963
Originally issued  on the album Page One

3 Out Of The Night 7:20 (Joe Henderson)
Joe Henderson - tenor saxaphone
Kenny Dorham - trumpet
McCoy Tyner - piano
Butch Warren - bass
Pete LaRoca - drums
Recorded on June 3, 1963

4 You Know I Care 7:15 (Duke Pearson)
Joe Henderson - tenor saxaphone
McCoy Tyner - piano
Bob Cranshaw - bass
Elvin Jones - drums
Recorded on November 30, 1964

5 As Me Now 5:53 (Thelonious Monk)
Joe Henderson - tenor saxaphone
Ron Carter - bass
Al Foster - drums
Recorded on November 14-16, 1985
Originally issued on the album The State Of The Tenor Volume One

6 Soulville 5:37 (Horace Silver)
Joe Henderson - tenor saxaphone
Ron Carter - bass
Al Foster - drums
Recorded on November 14-16, 1985
Originally issued on the album The State Of The Tenor Volume Two

7 Portrait 6:53 (Charles Mingus)
Joe Henderson - tenor saxaphone
Ron Carter - bass
Al Foster - drums
Recorded on November 14-16, 1985
Originally issued on the album The State Of The Tenor Volume Two
